<Action id="47083" issue="28518" author="sergey.minaev" type="comment" created="2018-07-09 08:15:14.0" updateauthor="sergey.minaev" updated="2018-07-09 08:16:13.0"> <body><! CDATA  ~ckochenower  yes, it's expected behavior Libindy waits responses from all validators to return single (aggregated) result to application. As one or more nodes are offline, the result will be returned on timeout (about 100sec, default timeout).  ></body> </Action>
